1- Setup environment

    - Install nextjs
        - npx create-next-app ./

    - Setup nextjs app
        - update layout
            - metadate
            - fonts

    -Eslint and prettier
        - install packages on vscode
        - npm install --save-dev eslint@8.57.0 eslint-config-next eslint-config-standard eslint-config-prettier eslint-plugin-tailwindcss eslint-plugin-unused-imports @typescript-eslint/parser
        - npm install --save-dev prettier @ianvs/prettier-plugin-sort-imports prettier-plugin-tailwindcss
        - create eslintrc and prettierrc files
        create .vscode/settings
